reviewText: For youth class room at church

I was not as impressed with this video as i expected to be. I thought the video did not explain the story of the last supper as thoroughly as it could have. For newcomers to the stories from Passion Week, this is not the best tool out there.
I love it.  I have the older Superbooks and they are a joy to view. But these are even more joyful because they have more actions and the puppeteers are dynamic!
Very good Bible series. My son loves it.

All of the SuperBook movies are of highest quality animation and storyline! Hope to own the entire collection. We watch them as a family and find them delightful and Biblically accurate. Well done CBN!!!!
